  "body": "How can I test the else path of this method?\r\nI did not find a way to change the chainid during an test.\r\n```\r\nfunction DOMAIN_SEPARATOR() public view override returns (bytes32) {\r\n\t\treturn\r\n\t\t\tblock.chainid == _domainSeperatorChainId\r\n\t\t\t\t? _domainSeperator\r\n\t\t\t\t: _calculateDomainSeparator(block.chainid);\r\n\t}\r\n```\r\nI am just curious, it is not that important. but 100% test coverage would be awesome ^^.",
